metadata.name: Musician Brothers
metadata.description:
Şerif and Hasip brothers have been playing music at weddings since childhood. Their fathers and grandfathers also come from the same profession. They are highly sought-after musicians in their region and surrounding areas. The photo was taken in 2012, when the two brothers were retiring. Unfortunately, neither of them are alive today.

Photography was selected first in the People category in the National Geographic Turkey National Photography Contest. World-renowned photography master Ara Güler was also on the jury of the competition.

Dimensions: 5315x3543 px, 300 DPI, 1/1
